.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.douban.com/people/ahbei/\&quot; class=\&quot; wrap external\&quot; target=\&quot;_blank\&quot; rel=\&quot;nofollow noreferrer\&quot;&gt;阿北&lt;i class=\&quot;icon-external\&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;很值得关注。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=\&quot;https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//swaroopch.com/notes/python/\&quot; class=\&quot; wrap external\&quot; target=\&quot;_blank\&quot; rel=\&quot;nofollow noreferrer\&quot;&gt;A Byte of Python&lt;i class=\&quot;icon-external\&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;：即简明Python教程，边看边练习就对Python有基本的了解，可以轻松存活。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=\&quot;https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//blog.hartleybrody.com/google-python/\&quot; class=\&quot; wrap external\&quot; target=\&quot;_blank\&quot; rel=\&quot;nofollow noreferrer\&quot;&gt;Google&#x27;s Python Lessons&lt;i class=\&quot;icon-external\&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;：Google出品的Python教程，值得信赖。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=\&quot;https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.python.org/doc/\&quot; class=\&quot; wrap external\&quot; target=\&quot;_blank\&quot; rel=\&quot;nofollow noreferrer\&quot;&gt;Python Documentation&lt;i class=\&quot;icon-external\&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;：Python在线文档，若嫌枯燥，可以直接看&lt;a href=\&quot;https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//docs.python.org/2/library/\&quot; class=\&quot; wrap external\&quot; target=\&quot;_blank\&quot; rel=\&quot;nofollow noreferrer\&quot;&gt;Python Standard Lib&lt;i class=\&quot;icon-external\&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=\&quot;https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//matrix.42qu.com/10757179\&quot; class=\&quot; wrap external\&quot; target=\&quot;_blank\&quot; rel=\&quot;nofollow noreferrer\&quot;&gt;42区：python入门指引&lt;i class=\&quot;icon-external\&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;：江湖人称&lt;a href=\&quot;https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//zuroc.42qu.com/\&quot; class=\&quot; wrap external\&quot;